    <item>
      <title>舒默推迟在关闭立场上反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/schumer-postpones-book-tour-amid-backlash-on-shutdown-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院民主党领导人查克·舒默（Chuck Schumer）推迟了本周计划的书之旅，因为他决定结束对共和党支出计划的封锁计划，以避免关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/schumer-postpones-book-tour-amid-backlash-on-shutdown-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 14:33:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的驱逐出境推动了法院检查其权力的能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/venezuelan-deportations-tests-courts-ability-to-check-trump-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政府在迅速驱逐了数百名委内瑞拉帮派成员，主张宣传宣传强大的权力来履行硬线移民政策后，被指控违反司法机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/venezuelan-deportations-tests-courts-ability-to-check-trump-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 14:01:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>改革英国诱饵29个叛逃的议员，因为法拉奇获得了地面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/reform-uk-lures-29-defecting-councilors-as-farage-gains-ground</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奈杰尔·法拉奇（Nigel Farage）揭幕了29名新议员＆mdash;包括十多个保守派叛逃者＆mdash;加入英国改革的人，作为一项新调查，他强调了他的政党如何在英国选民中受到关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/reform-uk-lures-29-defecting-councilors-as-farage-gains-ground</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 13:42:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯承诺要偿还英国借来的福利反弹的增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/reeves-pledges-to-get-a-grip-on-uk-debt-as-welfare-split-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）为自己的财政规则辩护，并承诺降低政府借贷，因为英国国库总理面临着反对削减福利支付和政府支出的工党同事的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/reeves-pledges-to-get-a-grip-on-uk-debt-as-welfare-split-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 13:23:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京允许一些西方资金出售俄罗斯证券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/putin-allows-some-western-funds-to-sell-russian-securities-m8d32339</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）在计划与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在乌克兰战争中与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）进行会谈的前一天，允许包括美国票房的一些国际资金出售俄罗斯证券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/putin-allows-some-western-funds-to-sell-russian-securities-m8d32339</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 13:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼（Carney）试图将法国拉近，英国更近，特朗普提出了更多的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/carney-tries-to-pull-france-uk-closer-with-more-tariffs-coming-from-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）在加拿大总理（Canada）担任首相的第一次国际旅行与欧洲盟友建立了更紧密的联盟，因为该国旨在减少对日益敌对的美国的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/carney-tries-to-pull-france-uk-closer-with-more-tariffs-coming-from-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 12:47:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟制裁卢旺达军事官员对刚果冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/rwanda-severs-diplomatic-relations-with-belgium</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，欧洲联盟批准了三名卢旺达军事官员和一家金炼油厂，因为批评基加利对M23民兵的支持在数十年来的最新冲突中占领了刚果东部民主共和国东部民主共和国的两个主要城市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/rwanda-severs-diplomatic-relations-with-belgium</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 11:19:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
